{
  "texts": [
    "However, all metrics adopted are viable for the classification task.",
    "Computational Complexity (F5) and Caveats (F9)The choice of an XAI method should consider its time, memory, and computational complexity constraints.",
    "In text classification, the number of features is typically very high.",
    "Not all the XAI methods presented scale well beyond certain amount of features regarding computational times and memory requirements.",
    "In the \"Objective Evaluation\" section, we will present the results of four different runs, in which we consider respectively the 10, 100, 1000 and 10,000 most common features of the corpus."
  ]
}